rovide concrete examples showing that C\u2019s communication issues have led to crew\u2011resource\u2011management breakdowns, or that A\u2019s unorganized behavior has resulted in missed procedural steps, that could shift the balance. Otherwise, I would move my vote to **Candidate\u202fC**.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
